Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:34.88,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}utsuro na yume aimai na shoudou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:39.35,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}yasashiku chi wo mitasu yorokobi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:42.79,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}nozomareta kaihou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:47.99,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}shinpiteki na kakusei no shunkan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:54.63,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}atatakaku afuredashi hizami yuku zanzou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:58.14,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ryoute de me wo fusagi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:02.34,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}hikari no subete wo tachikittara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:05.74,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}anata no koe wo sagasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:10.25,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}shikumareta kono kiseki e to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:15.99,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}tsunagaru shinri sono subete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:18.69,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}azayaka na keshiki
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:20.36,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}mujun teiri
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.63,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}risei wo koeru sentaku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:27.07,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}tsumi wo utai semeuru you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:29.84,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}yami wa iki wo korosu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:33.17,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}utsukushi no mon wo kuguru mono ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:36.08,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}torikawasareta keiyaku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:40.28,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}hirari hirari chou no izanai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:46.59,Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(0,2000)}yagate sakebi wa mutsuu ni kawaru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:34.88,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Um sonho vazio, um impulso ambíguo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:39.35,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A alegria de gentilmente satisfazer-se com sangue;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:42.79,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}a libertação desejada.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:47.99,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No momento do misterioso despertar,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:54.63,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}o vertente calor distorce as imagens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:58.14,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cobrindo meus olhos com as mãos,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:02.34,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}eu bloqueio toda a luz
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:05.74,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}e saio a procura da sua voz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:10.25,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Toda a verdade está conectada
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:15.99,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}a esse milagre arranjado.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:18.69,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Um vívido cenário,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:20.36,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}um inconsistente teorema
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.63,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}e escolhas que transcendem a razão.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:27.07,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Recitando um pecado à condenação,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:29.84,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}a escuridão aguarda em antecipação.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:33.17,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}O contrato é assinado por aqueles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:36.08,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}que atravessam o portão da beleza.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:40.28,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Vibrando levemente, as borboletas o convidam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:46.59,Tradução,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(0,2000)}Em breve os gritos se transformarão sem dor.
